{"tid":664431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［急不及待想玩玩了］「成蟲」做主角 台灣桌遊《誰是強國人》遭封殺","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T06:27:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f80283a5ba0638d9b5827b484022877e2eaeb2c3","tid":664431,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"大富翁相信好多人都玩過，但其實呢種千變萬化嘅桌上遊戲，唔係淨係擲骰咁簡單，仲有好多唔同寓意，好似出晒名做政治惡搞桌遊「美麗島風雲」嘅台灣公司，近日就推出咗名為《誰是強國人》嘅桌遊，內容影射港澳台同西藏被中國吞噬嘅情況，最尾當然引起中國不滿，仲連高雄舉辦嘅月光桌遊節都因為有中國廠商施壓而被迫退出，但另一邊廂，網上眾籌活動反應就非常熱烈，雖然仲有幾日先截止，但就已經比起原定集資額超出5倍。<br />\n<br />\n《誰是強國人》嘅遊戲背景係喺2050年，一陣又一陣蟲型黑影，不停掠過霧霾之中。玩家可以選擇「熱烈歡迎強國同胞」同「堅壁清野防守到底」兩種策略，而每個國家登場人物亦有唔同設定，好似係港澳版圖，就有一男一女，男嘅就手持雨傘，女嘅就以女荷官造型示人，至於強國壞蛋角色亦有唔少映射，其中有怪獸就引用咗影星成龍嘅金句：「中國人是要管」做藍本，當然玩家可以選擇歸邊或者抗爭對底，淨係呢個題目都已經吸引咗唔少人「課金」，喺眾籌平台度畀錢支持，原定籌眾目標嘅$92,197台幣，但截至5月13日下晝「善款」已經去到$58萬台幣，佢哋仲話只要去到$60萬，所有捐款者仲可以得到以遊戲設定為藍本嘅5萬字實體小說。<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇：Philip Chan：本來中國佬唔搞屎棍可能籌唔到呢個數<br />\n<br />\nSiu Chung Au：「港澳⋯等國家」，如果我說心動，會否犯上暴動罪？<br />\n<br />\n邱竟瑋：或許遊戲設定中有「幫忙強國的港、澳人士」存在。這樣比較符合現實狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/133150_e808fe27c59b4a2c530ab9fb6b6250c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F133150_e808fe27c59b4a2c530ab9fb6b6250c4.png&h=56873ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/133152_f0c617e244f890c8cec1b727849cb081.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F133152_f0c617e244f890c8cec1b727849cb081.png&h=615501e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/133155_6b6214b57492089212177a48cfb1031d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F133155_6b6214b57492089212177a48cfb1031d.png&h=38c51a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/133157_f0530a851bdbd29487ccda78a6354f39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F133157_f0530a851bdbd29487ccda78a6354f39.png&h=53789334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/133159_5052d62538afa1534b26fbbaf411901e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F133159_5052d62538afa1534b26fbbaf411901e.png&h=23606c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58187814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58187814&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1c484a1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F58187814&h=e27f32e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180514/58187814</a>"},{"pid":"66287d9004f87be61f5aaa6145592013eb193b09","tid":664431,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"EDC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea0601d6426370c47fb56f4f7fe92ffb5ee74dd","tid":664431,"uid":133529,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"屌，點支持?"},{"pid":"e020dad533d91f67a556020bcea9f3fab76c09aa","tid":664431,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"遊戲畫面呢?"},{"pid":"3874d4f4d203967f1682081c5f2eefd3eceb5b7e","tid":664431,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"重強國，叫贏國人喇"},{"pid":"a6b34b5838c0125f5ed24550540e0fdf47143b43","tid":664431,"uid":67551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3874d4f4d203967f1682081c5f2eefd3eceb5b7e","tid":664431,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite